Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,globe to the right of the device
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you see in the Devices
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't see a globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that means that it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,connected right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's asleep in your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Build and run to it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll connect to it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a little bit about how
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to get started with wireless
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,development.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But enough talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here I am with my Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a phone.
