Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see here's our new
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I check that the device and
