Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,icon appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's next after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to pull the plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So we see the phone is
