Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the globe icon, and that lets
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you know that you're ready to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,development.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to open an app that
