Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the README.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For now I'm going to click the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Play button.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This will build the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It will run, it will install and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,will launch the app and attach
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the debugger, and it will do all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of that completely wirelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the SolarSystem app provides
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a way for users to explore the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,solar system in a fun and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,interactive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So as soon as it comes up, we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,take a quick look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So here are our planets orbiting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been working on a fun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,feature called Moon Jumper.
