Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,wireless development.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Well, you got it plugged
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in, right, so you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pick it up and you're going to
